OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSexual violence: 100       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffestivals commit to        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftackling the issue         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 100 UK festivals - including 
OL,6, Parklife and Boardmasters - have       
OL,7, committed to tackling sexual violence. 
OL,9,FThe festivals have pledged to take a   
OL,10,Fsurvivor-led approach and that all     
OL,11,Fallegations will be taken seriously.   
OL,13,FDr Hannah Bows from Durham University  
OL,14,Fsaid research has shown sexual violence
OL,15,Fis a "common experience for festival   
OL,16,Fattendees - especially for women" and  
OL,17,Fis "often minimised or ignored".       
OL,19,FThe criminal law professor said the    
OL,20,Fmove was an "important first step".    
